=== play_absolute.glp ===
Four-actor play with absolute time targets.
Goal: play_absolute(VA?, VB?, VC?, VD?, Log?)

Alice acts immediately, Bob at T0+50ms, Carol at T0+100ms, Diana at T0+150ms.
Uses guard_sub for computing wait deltas from absolute targets.
Streams merged, observed, logged, then sent to accumulator monitor.

Actors:
- alice: add(10), add(5), value(VA)
- bob_at: wait(50), subtract(3), value(VB)
- carol_at: wait(100), add(20), value(VC)
- diana_at: wait(150), value(VD)
